tags.name: Namche Sagarmatha Murrphy helipad
tags.note: Very indistinct on Bing imagery. Confirmed on Google Maps, see "Website" link.

Manby helicopters flying to and from Lukla land here. In April 2019, a plane taking off at nearby Tenzing-Hillary Airport crashed into two helicopters at the helipad there. See https://avherald.com/h?article=4c6ab4e7.
